  <scopecontent id="aspace_a978553609c9f0c8ba5c9d20d026be66">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes State University of New York correspondence, minutes of administrative staff, and other materials; records of the Cornell Faculty Senate; material on physical biology, 1957-1964; records of the Veterinary College Council; material on new Veterinary College buildings; budget requests and related records; date books and calendars; records of veterinarians' conferences; Association of American Veterinary Medicine Colleges material; American Veterinary Medical Association correspondence; traditional Christmas letters from the Dean to alumni, 1959-1973; and other records of George C. Poppensiek as Dean of the New York State College of Veterinary Medicine.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_9eaaff584173d93c29e177e4f4740d99">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Records of the Office of the Dean, New York State College of Veterinary Medicine, #24-1-1646. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
